installing on a new machine:

- install the needed dependencies:

pip
django (through pip)
south (through pip)
pycountry (through pip)
python-pyparsing
python-lxml
python-tables
python-imaging
gdal-bin
python-gdal
python-mapscript
libapache2-mod-wsgi
cgi-mapserver
mapserver-bin

- copy the g2system.conf file from the apache directory to 
/etc/apache2/sites-available and make the necessary adjustments 
to the paths defined in the file

- enable the site with sudo a2ensiste g2system.conf


for monitoring apache2 logs:

tail -f /var/log/apache2/error.log
